## Findings & Fixes

### 1. `buildCssVars()` / `injectBranding()` inconsistency (fixed)
`BrandingContext.tsx:injectBranding()` mapped `--color-badge-teal` and `--color-gold` to `accentColor`, while the layout's `buildCssVars()` used `buttonColor`. Aligned context to match layout.

### 2. BottomNav hardcoded icon colors (fixed)
All 7 SVG icons used hardcoded `stroke='#2D6B73'` / `'#94A3B880'`. Changed to `stroke="currentColor"` with Tailwind classes (`text-gold` / `text-brown/50`) so they respond to `--color-gold` and `--color-text-secondary` overrides.

### 3. TopBar hardcoded icon colors (fixed)
All 4 SVG icons used `stroke="#1E293B"`. Changed to `stroke="currentColor"` with `className="text-navy"` so they respond to `--color-text-primary`.

### 4. QR code hardcoded color (fixed)
`QrContent.tsx` generated QR codes with hardcoded `#1E293B`. Now reads the computed `--color-text-primary` CSS variable at render time.

### 5. globals.css hardcoded background (fixed)
`html, body` and `#app-shell` used raw `#E8E0D4`. Changed to `var(--color-background, #E8E0D4)` so the outer shell also follows white-label branding.

