- `EngagementContent.tsx` ‚Äî correctly uses `var(--color-gold, #2D6B73)` inline with fallbacks
- Tailwind config ‚Äî properly references all CSS variables with fallbacks
- Layout's `buildCssVars()` ‚Äî correctly applies inline `style` to the wrapper div
- `BrandingProvider` context ‚Äî properly passes branding data to child components
